sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor Buyer
  participant API as Buyer API
  participant Audit as audit-requests-master
  participant Artifact as audit-artifacts
  participant TQ as templateQuestions
  participant AQ as auditQuestions
  actor Auditor
  actor Supplier
  participant Vault as DocVault / evidence
  participant Comp as Compliance Engine
  participant Report as audit-reports
  participant CAPA as capas
  participant Notify as Notification Orchestrator
  Buyer->>API: POST /api/buyer/audit-request
  API->>Audit: create audit request header
  API->>Artifact: create intimation / PAQ artifacts
  API->>Notify: emit notifications
  Auditor->>API: POST /api/auditor/create-draft-questions
  API->>TQ: load selected template questions
  API->>AQ: upsert generated execution questions
  API->>Audit: questionnaireStatus=in_progress
  Auditor->>API: POST /api/audits/:auditId/artifacts/:artifactId/send
  API->>Artifact: mark questionnaire sent
  API->>Audit: questionnaireStatus=sent_to_supplier
  Supplier->>API: PUT /api/auditor/audit-question/update-data/:auditRequestId
  API->>AQ: save supplier responses
  Supplier->>API: POST /api/digilocker/questions/:questionId/attach
  API->>Vault: create question-document mapping
  Auditor->>API: POST /api/auditor/audit-question/flag-follow-up
  API->>AQ: set flagStatus=auditor_flagged
  API->>Audit: questionnaireStatus=followup_requested
  Auditor->>API: POST /api/auditor/compliance/runs
  API->>Comp: snapshot responses and evaluate
  Auditor->>API: POST /api/auditor/audits/:auditId/report/draft
  API->>Report: upsert draft report
  Auditor->>API: POST /api/auditor/audits/:auditId/report/capas/generate
  API->>CAPA: create CAPAs from observations
  API->>AQ: back-link linkedCapaIds
  API->>Notify: emit milestone/status notifications
